{"tid":1038541,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有彈弓手應該點樣醫？","createTime":"2019-02-26T17:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T07:08:39.000Z","uid":157923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4af29bb9867ce40b915146d254d37d3ea6fa8466","tid":1038541,"uid":157923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T17:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啊媽做侍應<br />\n佢返工返到有彈弓手<br />\n之後叫佢唔好返都仲要返<br />\n搞到依家惡化<br />\n<br />\n重點係：佢繼續返工既原因係因為悶，搞到手惡化，嬲到我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人or 你識既人 曾經有患過彈弓手而好得番<br />\n可以話比我聽點樣醫好，同幾錢要醫幾耐？"},{"pid":"47cd396f2f269f8d3ae03ed8098e3d67504588e6","tid":1038541,"uid":118709,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T17:46:31.000Z","msg":"child 登 = 免費登記醫學咨詢"},{"pid":"b0985f43fcbb766a56ff45866b52bfc015e4b54f","tid":1038541,"uid":20619,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T17:49:38.000Z","msg":"唔好再猜包剪揼"},{"pid":"8891b1a8d5d309889e005b37136f236514410dd9","tid":1038541,"uid":104218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T17:55:48.000Z","msg":"拎住支筆芯 就唔會再怕彈弓"},{"pid":"994fd7b6c13cd6caae33a45f3c4d755908b0d0f9","tid":1038541,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T17:56:02.000Z","msg":"睇醫生<br />\n等排期做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1742d76bed38805c64b686aa571ad0cbae8dce9e","tid":1038541,"uid":168488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T17:58:01.000Z","msg":"過來人 睇醫生 物理治療 不停拉筋 停止工作 詳細pm"},{"pid":"cfcb3c4aff6747ad4b4d825e99f1644258b27a0e","tid":1038541,"uid":121245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"994fd7b6c13cd6caae33a45f3c4d755908b0d0f9","tid":1038541,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T17:56: